sentences: Dag Syver Arnesen (born 3 May 1950) is a Norwegian jazz pianist with a series of album releases.
Eventually he went to jazz and played in the 1970s with the Arvid Genius' orchestra, and led his own Trios, Quartets and Septetter og 13'tets.
His melodic style has been compared to Jan Johansson.
